                <h4 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-700 text-center mb-6">Deeper Dive</h4>
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                    <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-xl">
                        <h5 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-slate-800">ML Pipeline Explained</h5>
                        <p class="text-slate-600">The project followed a standard workflow: Data Preparation → Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) → Modeling → Evaluation. This structured approach ensures robust and reliable results.</p>
