                    <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-xl">
                        <h5 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-slate-800">Potential Enhancements</h5>
                        <p class="text-slate-600">To improve the 92.2% accuracy, we could use **Feature Engineering** to create more predictive inputs, **Hyperparameter Tuning** to optimize the model, and **Cross-Validation** for more robust evaluation.</p>
