                        <h5 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-slate-800">Advanced Models to Try</h5>
                        <p class="text-slate-600">While Random Forest performed well, state-of-the-art models like **XGBoost**, **LightGBM**, or even **Neural Networks** could potentially capture more complex patterns in the data and achieve even higher precision.</p>
